### 내부 상태 조회 (정상)
GET http://localhost:3001/internal/info
Accept: application/json

### 지연 테스트 (3초)
GET http://localhost:3001/internal/sleep?ms=3000
Accept: application/json

### 강제 실패 (500)
GET http://localhost:3001/internal/fail?code=500
Accept: application/json

### 잘못된 요청 (400)
GET http://localhost:3001/internal/fail?code=400
Accept: application/json